        {
            "title": "洪水橋#LYOS 簡潔雅廳明亮舒適 輕鐵站近咫尺",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"洪水橋#LYOS 簡潔雅廳明亮舒適 輕鐵站近咫尺\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/4e2f4a713fff1fb2b0164c9c1ce19f97/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250219/_2025021918012551129.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">洪水橋#LYOS 簡潔雅廳明亮舒適 輕鐵站近咫尺</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>洪水橋低密度屋苑#LYOS，入伙約2年，區內商店及食肆齊備，日常生活不假外求。今日介紹屋苑1C座高層B室，實用面積283方呎，1房間隔，附有企理裝修，望內園景，現時月租叫價13800元，實用呎租約48元。\n\n</p>\n<p>洪水橋新盤#LYOS位於洪水橋洪元路之上，由5座分層大樓組成，每座樓高5層，共341個單位。是次帶大家參觀該屋苑一個高層放盤，入屋即見長形廳堂，樓底特高，空間更為寬敞，配上雪白牆身及落地玻璃。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091040/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"洪水橋#LYOS 1C座高層B室，實用面積283方呎，現以月租13800元招租。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7c672112be1e0b572cf4543f0d039df2/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-19_at_4_31_12_PM_0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        洪水橋#LYOS 1C座高層B室，實用面積283方呎，現以月租13800元招租。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091041/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"開放式廚房前設置高枱，可作簡單用餐。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7931db919989e5d574f2e9b2f8e17ece/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-19_at_4_31_13_PM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        開放式廚房前設置高枱，可作簡單用餐。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091042/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"浴室潔具保養良好，設浴缸設備。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7dd3dc007a85db23cac21edef0b91812/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-19_at_4_31_13_PM_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        浴室潔具保養良好，設浴缸設備。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091043/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"寢室方正實用，設有闊窗。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/52764b9babe6681d032e684b8dea3750/2025-02/WhatsApp_Image_2025-02-19_at_4_31_13_PM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        寢室方正實用，設有闊窗。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4091053/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"洪水橋#LYOS外貌。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/129550d9f27a9dd6815352fdb3955aba/2025-02/PL240818LOS01.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        洪水橋#LYOS外貌。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>283呎1房開則</h2>\n<p>現時，客廳放置了長發、電視櫃等基本家具，走出露台，主要望寧靜內園景。而大廳一隅為開放式廚房，設有工作枱及廚櫃，備有煮食爐、抽油煙機等。放盤設有1間房，房間間隔四正，靠窗擺放大牀，旁邊有書桌連儲物櫃。\n\n</p>\n<p>由長實發展的#LYOS，鄰近洪福邨，亦毗鄰輕鐵洪水橋站，數分鐘步程即達。\n\n</p><h2>必睇靚位</h2>\n<p>樓齡新，入伙約2年\n\n</p>\n<p>廳房配備家具，即租即住\n\n</p>\n<p>單位樓底高，空間感強\n\n</p>\n<p>鄰近洪福商場及輕鐵洪水橋站\n\n</p><h2>放租單位資料</h2>\n<p>物業名稱：#LYOS\n\n</p>\n<p>地址：洪元路2號\n\n</p>\n<p>樓齡：2年\n\n</p>\n<p>單位：1C座高層B室\n\n</p>\n<p>實用面積：283方呎\n\n</p>\n<p>間隔：1房\n\n</p>\n<p>叫租：13800元\n\n</p>\n<p>呎租：48元\n\n</p>\n<p>代理行：中原地產\n\n</p>\n<p>電話：6895 0867（陳先生）\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
